text: Alexandre Briancon (born February 9, 1991) is a French figure skater. He is a two-season competitor on the Junior Grand Prix and placed 9th at the 2007 French Figure Skating Championships. He won the bronze medal at the 2007 European Youth Olympics. ==External links== * Category:French male single skaters Category:Living people Category:1991 births Category:Sportspeople from Annecy
